data.description: Live the island life on desirable Talahi Island!  This stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom gem nestled on an extra-large lot at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac, is the epitome of coastal living at its finest. This home offers ample space for your family and guests.  Master suite downstairs along with 2 guest bedrooms, in a desirable split-bedroom plan. Upstairs is spacious 4th bedroom/bonus room with it's own full bath, along with a separate office space.  Escape to your spacious backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding in tranquility. Enjoy access to the community dock, providing opportunities for boating, fishing, and fun. The heart of this home boasts a modern kitchen adorned with granite countertops, providing the perfect space for culinary adventures and hosting memorable gatherings. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this Talahi Island beauty your own.  $330,000 ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 2.75%!
